---
// SkipLink component - allows keyboard users to skip to main content
---

<a href="#main-content" class="skip-link"> Sauter au contenu principal </a>

<style>
  .skip-link {
    position: absolute;
    top: -40px;
    left: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    padding: 0.8rem 1.6rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    background: var(--accent);
    border-radius: 0 0 0.8rem;
  }

  .skip-link:focus {
    top: 0;
  }
</style>
